{"tid":565031,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"小迷妹的正確打開方式 看看這是不是看見TWICE的你？","createTime":"2018-02-18T15:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T12:18:13.000Z","uid":34643,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1248b00c7c51dbc4ac7d11ccf28ca567fe898a02","tid":565031,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"在gaon頒獎禮上想給IU李智恩送花的TWUCE林娜璉，雖然第一次失敗了，但是最後還是鼓足勇氣順利給了IU，IU在下班路上還一直拿著兔牙給的小花哦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2018/02/18/867a38ff5e44f4494bc277d658403eee1518922659.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F867a38ff5e44f4494bc277d658403eee1518922659.gif&h=ef46a0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2018/02/18/01188a8cd53c45c63ea2c30a1be866011518922667.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F01188a8cd53c45c63ea2c30a1be866011518922667.gif&h=4ac8857a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2018/02/18/ef2329754893631acefb053f345d4d221518922680.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2Fef2329754893631acefb053f345d4d221518922680.gif&h=0144cf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.idol001.com/origin/2018/02/18/b55752b294f0be6aa99b36381017c77a1518922687.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.idol001.com%2Forigin%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2Fb55752b294f0be6aa99b36381017c77a1518922687.gif&h=c1100915&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0c9d8fa932a569c6ddac6065f8ee347e0ac9ce4","tid":565031,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T15:04:28.000Z","msg":"不只我們會有一個欣賞追尋的偶像，其實就連現在線上的藝人們也是，其中TWICE娜璉就是歌手IU（ 、李知恩）的狂粉，在14日舉辦時《2017 GAON CHART AWARD》，見到偶像得獎的時候，特地拿著准備好的花朵送上，就連最後大合照也不想放過和偶像同框機會，在志效的幫忙之下才得以站在IU身後，相當可愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://t10.baidu.com/it/u=975287313,3129368987&amp;fm=173&amp;s=01F15997025A37DEC01AE2870300F08B&amp;w=600&amp;h=450&amp;img.JPEG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D975287313%2C3129368987%26fm%3D173%26s%3D01F15997025A37DEC01AE2870300F08B%26w%3D600%26h%3D450%26img.JPEG&h=59e3f809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲娜璉是IU的小粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n《2017 GAON CHART AWARD》14日於蠶室室內體育館舉行，其中在IU連續獲得「年度長存獎」和「作詞人獎」時，可以從TWICE粉絲側拍的影片中發現，在IU獲得第一個獎項時，定延一直想將娜璉推出去做些什麼的模樣，不過卻因為害羞和時機錯過了，娜璉還輕敲了自己頭一下似乎相當懊悔，其他成員看見這個模樣也忍不住笑了出來。<br />\n<br />\n而就在「作詞人獎」頒獎人GOT7 珍榮喊出IU名字的同時，娜璉馬上以最快的速度起身跨越彩锳，直直走出圓桌邊邊等待時機將手上的向日葵給IU，對方一發現也笑著收下，終於送成功的娜璉一開始身體還有些僵硬，轉頭低下頭害羞地笑了起來，TWICE其他成員們也都很替她感到開心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://t11.baidu.com/it/u=2551752793,1713451332&amp;fm=173&amp;s=A8F0C3074C73BCD40535499F03009086&amp;w=398&amp;h=450&amp;img.JPEG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D2551752793%2C1713451332%26fm%3D173%26s%3DA8F0C3074C73BCD40535499F03009086%26w%3D398%26h%3D450%26img.JPEG&h=8d6355be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲娜璉把握機會送IU花朵，成功後低頭羞笑。<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，在最後大合照時娜璉一發現IU就站在TWICE旁邊的位置，因為自己站得離對方有點遠，就露出有些猶豫又害羞的表情，最後忍不住跟團員們說自己站到IU後面一起合照的願望，最後在智效的幫忙之下成功走過去，忍不住大笑了起來，在攝影師准備拍照的同時，也比著大大的愛心表達喜悅之意，小迷妹的模樣也讓粉絲直呼好可愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://t12.baidu.com/it/u=1448723942,2062998112&amp;fm=173&amp;s=E9D07085CAE08ED816C8759E0300C081&amp;w=500&amp;h=833&amp;img.JPEG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D1448723942%2C2062998112%26fm%3D173%26s%3DE9D07085CAE08ED816C8759E0300C081%26w%3D500%26h%3D833%26img.JPEG&h=b5c757f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲娜璉偷站到IU身後。"},{"pid":"d08570746d773a7622b2dc3791f9de3bfefcb5de","tid":565031,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33a6057617aad2b81607c7ac2a28028b4ce3bed","tid":565031,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚多韓星好鍾意我老婆"},{"pid":"b1f343c976bca638460a6c56689d05f09675d7f7","tid":565031,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce8d30e33d069cdc64095d4841885ce757976b21","tid":565031,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b1f343c976bca638460a6c56689d05f09675d7f7","tid":565031,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09:09:49.000Z","msg":"第1張圖第一次送花唔成功<br />\n第2張圖畀隊友扑頭<br />\n第34張圖第二次送花成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7d92555c78a3344f849472da61f1e5d42374b0","tid":565031,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09:56:20.000Z","msg":"送花搏見報上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc20163597d558d09e6895ed25286f586e77a4b","tid":565031,"uid":76632,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce8d30e33d069cdc64095d4841885ce757976b21","tid":565031,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b1f343c976bca638460a6c56689d05f09675d7f7","tid":565031,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09:09:49.000Z","msg":"第1張圖第一次送花唔成功<br />\n第2張圖畀隊友扑頭<br />\n第34張圖第二次送花成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:18:13.000Z","msg":"我都想俾定延扑頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji